ow.                            </p>                            <p>Our conference tends to draw highly motivated individuals that have already made impacts in their communities and will undoubtedly continue to do so in the future.                             We look forward to your joining us in this exciting journey and experience all that UCBMUN and San Francisco has to offer!                                                                                     <p>Respectfully,<br>                            Akash Sharma<br>                            Secretary-General<br>                            UCBMUN XIX                            </p>                        </div>                    </div>                </div>                </div>            </div>        </div>        <!-- Le Javascript to prevent blocking -->        <script type="text/javascript" src="http://code.jquery.com/jquery.min.js"></script>        <script src = "js/script.js"></script>                <script type="text/javascript" src= "js/smoothscroll.js"></script>                     </body></html>